						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone on the tank bund.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription states that <hi rend="bold">Narase-Nāyaka</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Kāṁkati,</hi> made a grant of land at <hi rend="bold">Haligeṟe</hi> for the offerings to a goddess (name lost).</p>						

						<p>The details of the date preserved in the record, <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> <hi rend="bold">Śaka 132 Jyēshṭha ba. 30 • • • • • solar eclipse,</hi> are insufficient to find out the equivalent.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
